item.title: If someone can help me create server i will give 20mil on runescape.com
item.dc:creator: @Kastro1 Kastro_
item.description:
@Kastro1 wrote:

Instead of requesting, why don’t you try learning how to make one yourself? There’s like 100 tutorials explaining how to start off.

Personally the first thing I would do is start reading on some Java documents, once you think you’ve understood the concept then move onto download a simple source/client - this can be found in “Server Downloads“ section in this forum. Once you’ve downloaded it, play around so add npcs, add commands, change the home etc.
